snippet.title: 【Lyric MV】Fortina "Ⅵ. THE SWORD" (Full Ver.) 【MementoMori】
snippet.description:
This is a Lament (original character theme song) from MementoMori, a new RPG that released on 10.18.2022.

==================================
A girl who closed off her loving heart
when her best friend betrayed her.
“Fortina”
==================================
